OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1775664666
OL,3,CDrink-drive crackdown at ferry
OL,4,Cterminal sees zero drivers over the
OL,5,Climit
OL,7,FAn operation targeting drink drivers
OL,8,Farriving in Dorset by ferry has
OL,9,Fresulted in no arrests, police have
OL,10,Fsaid.
OL,12,FOfficers from Dorset Police's Roads
OL,13,FPolicing Team stopped 97 vehicles as
OL,14,Fthey disembarked from the 4pm from
OL,15,FCherbourg at Poole on Tuesday evening.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
