OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1775664666
OL,3,CDrink-drive crackdown at ferry
OL,4,Cterminal sees zero drivers over the
OL,5,Climit
OL,7,FAround 30 drivers were breathalysed
OL,8,Fduring the hour-long operation, in a
OL,9,Ffirst of its kind for the force. While
OL,10,Fsome had consumed alcohol onboard,
OL,11,Fnone were found to be over the legal
OL,12,Fdrink-drive limit.
OL,14,FPolice said the campaign is designed
OL,15,Fnot only to catch offenders, but to
OL,16,Fact as a deterrent to those tempted to
OL,17,Fdrink alcohol during ferry or plane
OL,18,Fjourneys before driving home.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1775664666
OL,3,CDrink-drive crackdown at ferry
OL,4,Cterminal sees zero drivers over the
OL,5,Climit
OL,7,FInspector Lee Turner said: "We know
OL,8,Fthat enjoying a drink while on a plane
OL,9,For ferry can be part of the holiday
OL,10,Fexperience, but some people can get
OL,11,Fcarried away and forget they still
OL,12,Fneed to drive home.
OL,14,F"Driving while under the influence of
OL,15,Falcohol, coupled with fatigue from
OL,16,Ftravelling, can have a significant
OL,17,Feffect on a person's ability to drive
OL,18,Fand react to hazards. The message is
OL,19,Fvery clear - if you are planning on
OL,20,Fdrinking, make sure you are not the
OL,21,Fdesignated driver."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1775664666
OL,3,CDrink-drive crackdown at ferry
OL,4,Cterminal sees zero drivers over the
OL,5,Climit
OL,7,FDorset Police and Crime Commissioner
OL,8,FDavid Sidwick said there is "never an
OL,9,Fexcuse" for getting behind the wheel
OL,10,Fwhile intoxicated and thanked officers
OL,11,Ffor their work keeping the county's
OL,12,Froads safe.
OL,14,FAlthough no drivers were over the
OL,15,Flimit, officers said some had been
OL,16,Fdrinking but recorded legal readings.
OL,17,FThey were advised about the effects
OL,18,Falcohol can still have on reaction
OL,19,Ftimes and driving ability.
OL,26,@pD@]OUqD@GO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/6
