OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1775664666
OL,3,CDrink-drive crackdown at ferry
OL,4,Cterminal sees zero drivers over the
OL,5,Climit
OL,7,FSergeant Dave Cotterill said it was
OL,8,Fencouraging that the message about the
OL,9,Fdangers of drink driving appeared to
OL,10,Fbe getting through.
OL,12,FThe operation was launched at the Port
OL,13,Fof Poole and will be expanded in the
OL,14,Fcoming days to include Bournemouth
OL,15,FAirport.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/6
